41:20.228 --> 41:22.765
What if they need our help?

41:22.855 --> 41:24.470
We have to find them.

41:24.565 --> 41:25.565
Wait, wait, what?

41:25.608 --> 41:26.723
No, but stoick said...

41:26.818 --> 41:28.024
It doesn't matter what he said

41:28.111 --> 41:29.271
if they've all been captured.

41:29.362 --> 41:30.522
Come on!

41:34.409 --> 41:35.615
Do we go back?

41:35.702 --> 41:37.238
We've nowhere to go,

41:37.328 --> 41:40.286
nothing to sell, and no heads
to call our own.

41:40.373 --> 41:41.829
- Uh, eret...?
- If we don't turn up

41:41.916 --> 41:44.328
with dragons and fast...

41:45.837 --> 41:47.702
Careful what you wish for!

41:47.797 --> 41:49.253
- Do something!
- Eret, son of eret!

41:49.340 --> 41:50.580
We'll miss you, eret!

41:50.675 --> 41:51.585
What is this?

41:51.676 --> 41:52.676
A kidnapping.

41:52.719 --> 41:54.300
Yay, can he ride with me?
Can he?

41:54.387 --> 41:55.422
Can he...?

41:56.973 --> 41:58.884
You're gonna show us
the way to drago.

41:58.975 --> 42:02.092
And help dragon riders
sneak into drago's camp?

42:02.186 --> 42:03.221
Just kill me now.

42:03.312 --> 42:04.312
That could be arranged.

42:04.397 --> 42:05.807
Stormfly, drop it.

42:05.898 --> 42:07.513
Huh?

42:08.484 --> 42:09.815
Good girl!

42:09.902 --> 42:12.894
Stormfly, fetch.

42:13.948 --> 42:14.948
All right!

42:15.033 --> 42:17.866
Okay! I'll take you to drago!

42:19.871 --> 42:21.486
Works every time.

42:29.756 --> 42:32.247
Hey, I-l thought
we were going to eat.

42:32.341 --> 42:34.047
Oh, we are.

43:04.749 --> 43:08.116
And then, from dragon island,
I found this archipelago...

43:15.134 --> 43:16.874
There.

43:16.969 --> 43:19.551
Whoa.

44:09.272 --> 44:11.183
Oh, when I'm up here,

44:11.274 --> 44:12.935
I don't even feel the cold.

44:13.025 --> 44:14.390
I just feel...

44:14.485 --> 44:15.850
Free.

44:19.574 --> 44:24.489
This is what it is
to be a dragon, hiccup.

44:25.204 --> 44:26.535
It's all well and good

44:26.622 --> 44:27.862
to call yourself a dragon,

44:27.957 --> 44:29.197
but can you fly?

44:50.771 --> 44:52.307
Oh, no! Aah!

45:03.075 --> 45:04.485
Man, almost!

45:04.577 --> 45:06.722
We just about had it that time.

45:12.084 --> 45:13.324
Incredible.

45:14.295 --> 45:16.001
Well, not bad yourself.

45:26.349 --> 45:29.716
All this time,
you took after me.

45:29.810 --> 45:31.596
And...

45:31.687 --> 45:33.018
Where was I?

45:35.399 --> 45:37.640
I'm so sorry, hiccup.

45:37.735 --> 45:40.147
Can we start over?

45:44.158 --> 45:45.898
Will you give me another chance?

45:48.496 --> 45:50.862
I-1 can teach you
all that I've learned

45:50.957 --> 45:53.824
these past 20 years.

45:53.918 --> 45:55.579
Like...

45:59.924 --> 46:01.004
Wow.

46:01.092 --> 46:03.333
Now you can make
those tight turns.

46:06.430 --> 46:07.545
Did you know about this?

46:07.640 --> 46:10.052
Every dragon

46:10.142 --> 46:12.383
has its secrets. And...

46:12.478 --> 46:14.389
I'll show them all to you.

46:15.022 --> 46:16.853
We'll unlock every mystery,

46:16.941 --> 46:19.933
find every last species...
Together, as mother and son.

46:26.701 --> 46:30.990
This gift we share, hiccup,
it bonds us.

46:31.831 --> 46:35.073
This is who you are, son.

46:35.167 --> 46:36.748
Who we are.

46:36.836 --> 46:40.624
We will change the world
for all dragons.

46:40.715 --> 46:43.297
We will make it a better,
safer place.

46:43.384 --> 46:44.794
Yeah, I mean,

46:44.885 --> 46:47.342
that sounds amazing.

46:59.442 --> 47:01.398
On, this is so great!

47:01.485 --> 47:04.602
Now you and I can go talk
to drago together.

47:04.697 --> 47:06.062
What?

47:06.157 --> 47:08.318
There's no talking to drago.

47:08.409 --> 47:09.694
