- No.

47:09.785 --> 47:12.071
We must protect our own.

47:12.163 --> 47:13.243
Come on.

47:13.331 --> 47:14.662
We should be getting back.

47:15.583 --> 47:16.618
Hmm?

47:29.638 --> 47:31.754
Okay, I got you here!

47:31.849 --> 47:33.089
Now get this thing off me.

47:33.184 --> 47:34.924
Never take a toy from a dragon.

47:35.019 --> 47:36.555
Don't you know anything?

47:37.980 --> 47:40.471
