I'm thinking

48:03.631 --> 48:05.542
class five leviathan,

48:05.633 --> 48:07.089
maybe six.

48:10.763 --> 48:12.594
Yah!

48:21.982 --> 48:23.622
- Meatlug, what's wrong, girl?
- Hookfang!

48:23.651 --> 48:26.609
- Don't move!
- Uh...

48:41.585 --> 48:42.700
