48:47.091 --> 48:48.171
Get off me!

48:50.344 --> 48:52.505
Always great
to see you, my friend.

48:52.596 --> 48:54.712
Keeping warm up here?

48:58.185 --> 49:00.767
Well, as you can see,
I am right on time

49:00.855 --> 49:02.766
with a new batch of dragons,

49:02.857 --> 49:03.937
just like I promised.

49:04.024 --> 49:05.810
- He's waking up!
- Drop the ropes!

49:05.901 --> 49:07.186
Give me some backup here!

49:07.278 --> 49:08.734
Watch out!

49:08.821 --> 49:10.231
Drop the ropes.

49:43.522 --> 49:45.041
- Hookfang!
- Hey!

49:45.065 --> 49:46.350
What are you doing?

49:46.859 --> 49:49.976
You belong to me now.

49:51.363 --> 49:53.524
And as an added bonus,

49:53.616 --> 49:56.028
I also caught you their riders.

49:56.118 --> 49:58.029
No extra charge. What?

49:58.120 --> 49:59.576
Are you kidding me? Aw!

49:59.663 --> 50:01.654
But you were so perfect!

50:01.749 --> 50:04.081
Turns out there's a whole bunch
of them out there.

50:04.168 --> 50:05.928
They attacked...

50:06.670 --> 50:07.750
How many?

50:07.838 --> 50:10.375
Drago doesn't have them
after all.

50:10.466 --> 50:11.797
- How many?
- Hundreds.

50:11.884 --> 50:13.294
A whole island full.

50:13.385 --> 50:15.341
I wouldn't worry about it.

50:15.429 --> 50:18.671
My men are
hunting them down as we speak.

50:18.766 --> 50:20.302
They won't know
where you're hiding.

50:20.392 --> 50:21.848
I promise you that.

50:21.936 --> 50:23.927
Oh, yes, they will!
They know we're missing,

50:24.021 --> 50:26.057
and they have tracking dragons.

50:26.148 --> 50:28.639
If you so much as touch us,
hiccup is gonna kick...

50:28.734 --> 50:30.599
- Hiccup?
- He's not a problem.

50:30.694 --> 50:32.685
Really, trust me.

50:32.780 --> 50:34.941
He's only the son
of stoick the vast,

50:35.032 --> 50:36.943
his heir to the throne of berk,

50:37.034 --> 50:40.618
and the greatest dragon master
this world has ever seen.

50:40.704 --> 50:42.660
