right now,

50:52.216 --> 50:54.628
he will blast through here
on his night fury

50:54.718 --> 50:58.131
and blow your entire
fleet of ships to splinters.

50:58.222 --> 50:59.712
Then they'll be crying
like babies.

50:59.807 --> 51:01.172
Funny and beautiful.

51:01.267 --> 51:02.598
Good one, babe.

51:02.685 --> 51:05.267
Like babies, they always cry.

51:05.354 --> 51:06.560
Real tiny ones.

51:06.647 --> 51:08.888
First there was one rider,

51:08.983 --> 51:11.520
and now all of berk?

51:12.403 --> 51:14.394
And you led them to me!

51:14.488 --> 51:16.979
Drago...!

51:17.074 --> 51:20.066
Stop all preparations!

51:20.160 --> 51:24.073
We must attack
the dragon riders' nest at once!

51:24.164 --> 51:27.577
We will take down their Alpha.

51:27.668 --> 51:31.377
Then we will take berk!

51:32.756 --> 51:34.166
Drago!

51:34.258 --> 51:35.498
And get rid of him.

51:35.593 --> 51:38.505
Drago, please, I...

51:44.101 --> 51:45.966
Stormfly!

51:49.440 --> 51:51.226
No!

52:02.119 --> 52:04.235
Well, bud...

52:04.330 --> 52:07.367
We can't wait around for drago
to attack this place.

52:07.458 --> 52:09.289
We've got to find him first.

52:16.592 --> 52:17.592
Let's go.

