Heads up!

1:03:33.435 --> 1:03:35.471
Dragon master.

1:03:36.396 --> 1:03:38.136
Welcome aboard, dragon rider.

1:03:38.231 --> 1:03:39.721
Thanks. I think.

1:03:39.816 --> 1:03:41.431
Where have you been?

1:03:41.526 --> 1:03:44.438
Oh, you know,
catching up with mom.

1:03:56.207 --> 1:03:57.822
That's your mother?

1:03:57.917 --> 1:04:00.533
Well, now you know
where I get my dramatic flair.

1:04:05.300 --> 1:04:06.836
The Alpha!

1:04:06.926 --> 1:04:09.212
Now we have a fight!

1:04:22.275 --> 1:04:24.561
Come on, toothless.

1:04:24.652 --> 1:04:26.734
Show them what you got, bud.

1:04:31.284 --> 1:04:32.615
Attaboy!

1:04:45.673 --> 1:04:48.039
I've waited
a long time for this.

1:04:48.134 --> 1:04:50.466
You cannot take our dragons!

1:04:50.553 --> 1:04:52.214
They are controlled
by the Alpha!

1:04:52.305 --> 1:04:55.138
Then it's a good thing
I brought a challenger.

1:05:18.289 --> 1:05:19.495
Another one?

1:05:19.582 --> 1:05:22.870
That is a class ten! Class ten!

1:05:22.961 --> 1:05:24.167
Look out!

1:05:26.798 --> 1:05:29.710
- No... no...
- Come on! Take down the Alpha!

1:05:49.070 --> 1:05:50.310
Thank you.

1:05:50.405 --> 1:05:51.736
For you, my dear...

1:05:51.823 --> 1:05:53.688
Anything.

1:06:01.040 --> 1:06:03.122
Val, do you think
you can stop them?

1:06:03.209 --> 1:06:05.700
I'll do my best.
Come on, cloudjumper!

1:06:05.795 --> 1:06:07.660
You!

1:06:07.755 --> 1:06:09.871
I watched you burn!

1:06:09.966 --> 1:06:12.298
It takes more than
a little fire to kill me!

1:06:35.033 --> 1:06:36.273
Stoick!

1:06:56.846 --> 1:06:58.006
No!

1:07:00.141 --> 1:07:01.972
No!

1:07:22.997 --> 1:07:24.453
We've won.

1:07:25.959 --> 1:07:27.540
Finish her!

1:07:27.627 --> 1:07:28.867
No!

1:07:37.011 --> 1:07:38.217
Hold on!

1:07:38.304 --> 1:07:39.544
Skullcrusher, go!

1:07:40.598 --> 1:07:41.758
Come on, gobber!

1:07:41.849 --> 1:07:44.056
Right behind you, stoick!

1:08:03.288 --> 1:08:04.494
Stop!

1:08:06.666 --> 1:08:07.906
Stop!

1:08:13.798 --> 1:08:17.757
This...
Is the great dragon master?

1:08:17.844 --> 1:08:20.176
The son of stoick the vast?

1:08:22.849 --> 1:08:25.556
What shame he must feel.

1:08:26.519 --> 1:08:28.225
All of this loss...

1:08:28.313 --> 1:08:29.894
And for what?

1:08:29.981 --> 1:08:31.892
To become unstoppable?

1:08:31.983 --> 1:08:34.144
To rule the world?

1:08:34.235 --> 1:08:38.194
Dragons, they-they are kind,
amazing creatures

1:08:38.281 --> 1:08:39.896
that can bring people together.

1:08:41.868 --> 1:08:43.779
Or tear them apart.

1:08:46.664 --> 1:08:49.155
You see, I know what it is

1:08:49.250 --> 1:08:51.832
to live in fear,

1:08:51.919 --> 1:08:54.581
to see my village burned,

1:08:54.672 --> 1:08:57.630
my family taken.

1:08:57.717 --> 1:08:59.799
But even as a boy...

1:09:00.428 --> 1:09:02.544
Left with nothing,

1:09:03.348 --> 1:09:07.307
I vowed to rise above
the fear of dragons...

1:09:09.520 --> 1:09:12.011
And liberate the people
of this world.

1:09:12.106 --> 1:09:14.438
Then why a dragon army?

1:09:14.525 --> 1:09:18.985
Well, you need dragons
to conquer other dragons.

1:09:19.072 --> 1:09:22.155
Or maybe you need dragons
to conquer people...

1:09:22.825 --> 1:09:25.032
To control those
who follow you...

1:09:25.995 --> 1:09:28.281
And to get rid
of those who won't.

1:09:30.958 --> 1:09:32.539
Clever boy.

1:09:32.627 --> 1:09:34.993
The world wants peace,

1:09:35.088 --> 1:09:38.171
and we have the answer
back on berk.

1:09:38.257 --> 1:09:40.293
Just... let me show you...

1:09:40.385 --> 1:09:41.670
No!

1:09:42.512 --> 1:09:44.127
Let me...

1:09:44.222 --> 1:09:46.178
Show you!

1:09:53.981 --> 1:09:54.981
What in...

1:10:00.488 --> 1:10:01.898
Hiccup!

1:10:01.989 --> 1:10:04.275
Come on, gobber!

1:10:04.367 --> 1:10:06.904
Okay, change of plan.

1:10:09.038 --> 1:10:12.576
No dragon can resist
the Alpha's command.

1:10:12.667 --> 1:10:16.660
So he who controls the Alpha...

1:10:16.754 --> 1:10:19.996
Controls them all.

1:10:22.468 --> 1:10:24.880
Toothless?

1:10:30.184 --> 1:10:32.550
T-toothless, you okay, bud?
What's going on?

1:10:32.645 --> 1:10:34.385
Witness true strength.

1:10:36.607 --> 1:10:39.690
The strength
of will over others.

1:10:44.532 --> 1:10:46.773
In the face of it,

1:10:46.868 --> 1:10:49.575
you are nothing.

1:10:53.791 --> 1:10:56.373
Uh... what did he just tell you?

1:11:00.214 --> 1:11:01.795
Toothless, come on.

1:11:01.883 --> 1:11:03.498
What's the matter with you?

1:11:03.593 --> 1:11:05.313
No, no, no, no, come on,
what are you doing?

1:11:05.344 --> 1:11:06.709
Knock it off.

1:11:06.804 --> 1:11:09.170
Stop! Snap out of it!

1:11:15.730 --> 1:11:17.436
Toothless, no!

1:11:17.523 --> 1:11:19.434
Toothless!

1:11:23.362 --> 1:11:24.852
- Don't!
- Hiccup!

1:11:26.324 --> 1:11:28.360
- Stop...!
- Son!

1:11:28.451 --> 1:11:29.451
Dad!

1:11:29.535 --> 1:11:30.775
No!

1:11:37.460 --> 1:11:38.540
Hmm.

1:11:49.847 --> 1:11:50.962
No...

1:11:59.106 --> 1:12:00.562
Dad!

1:12:00.650 --> 1:12:02.561
Stoick...

1:12:05.905 --> 1:12:07.361
Dad?

1:12:07.448 --> 1:12:09.234
No. You...

1:12:22.129 --> 1:12:23.369
No.

1:12:32.807 --> 1:12:34.843
No, no, no. No.

1:12:56.539 --> 1:12:58.245
No! Get away from him!

1:13:00.167 --> 1:13:01.623
Go on! Get out of here!

1:13:01.711 --> 1:13:04.373
Get away!

1:13:04.463 --> 1:13:07.421
It's not his fault.

1:13:07.508 --> 1:13:09.089
You know that.

1:13:15.850 --> 1:13:17.135
Good dragons

1:13:17.226 --> 1:13:19.592
under the control
of bad people...

1:13:19.687 --> 1:13:22.053
- No, wait. Don't go.
- Do bad things.

1:13:42.001 --> 1:13:43.241
Come on!

1:13:44.670 --> 1:13:47.002
Gather the men
and meet me at berk!

1:13:47.089 --> 1:13:49.751
- Toothless!
- No, don't.

1:14:15.868 --> 1:14:18.450
May the valkyries welcome you

1:14:18.537 --> 1:14:21.495
and lead you through
Odin's great battlefield.

1:14:22.541 --> 1:14:25.374
May they sing your name
with love and fury,

1:14:25.461 --> 1:14:28.794
so that we might hear it rise
from the depths of Valhalla,

1:14:29.340 --> 1:14:31.626
and know that you've taken
your rightful place

1:14:31.717 --> 1:14:34.049
at the table of kings.

1:14:35.596 --> 1:14:38.008
For a great man has fallen.

1:14:38.849 --> 1:14:40.134
A warrior.

1:14:41.102 --> 1:14:42.592
A chieftain.

1:14:42.687 --> 1:14:44.518
A father.

1:14:45.606 --> 1:14:46.812
A friend.

1:15:21.392 --> 1:15:23.132
I'm sorry, dad.

1:15:36.407 --> 1:15:38.068
I'm not the chief that...

1:15:38.159 --> 1:15:39.615
You wanted me to be.

1:15:40.327 --> 1:15:43.740
And I'm not the peacekeeper
I thought I was.

1:15:45.958 --> 1:15:48.324
L... don't know...

1:16:01.307 --> 1:16:04.219
You came early into this world.

1:16:04.310 --> 1:16:06.676
You were such a wee thing.

1:16:06.771 --> 1:16:10.389
On, so frail, so fragile.

1:16:10.483 --> 1:16:12.565
I feared you wouldn't make it.

1:16:14.695 --> 1:16:16.560
But your father...

1:16:17.656 --> 1:16:19.237
He never doubted.

1:16:20.159 --> 1:16:24.402
He always said you'd become
the strongest of them all.

1:16:24.497 --> 1:16:26.533
And he was right.

1:16:28.584 --> 1:16:30.996
You have the heart of a chief,

1:16:31.087 --> 1:16:33.328
and the soul of a dragon.

1:16:33.422 --> 1:16:36.914
Only you can bring
our worlds together.

1:16:38.052 --> 1:16:42.045
That... is who you are, son.

1:16:55.569 --> 1:16:56.934
I, uh...

1:16:58.030 --> 1:17:01.113
I was so afraid
of becoming my dad.

1:17:03.285 --> 1:17:06.027
Mostly because
I thought I never could.

1:17:06.122 --> 1:17:09.114
How-how do you become someone...

1:17:09.208 --> 1:17:11.620
That great, that... brave,

1:17:11.710 --> 1:17:14.247
that... selfless?

1:17:17.466 --> 1:17:20.333
I guess you can only try.

1:17:27.685 --> 1:17:30.722
A chief protects his own.

1:17:34.066 --> 1:17:35.806
We're going back.

1:17:37.027 --> 1:17:40.895
- Uh... with what?
- Uh, he took all the dragons.

1:17:40.990 --> 1:17:43.402
Not all of them.

1:17:47.163 --> 1:17:48.494
Whoal

1:17:48.581 --> 1:17:50.287
whoal! “Whoa!

1:17:50.374 --> 1:17:51.705
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

1:17:54.170 --> 1:17:55.455
I don't want to die!

1:17:55.546 --> 1:17:57.537
We can't fly these things!

1:17:57.631 --> 1:17:58.751
Yeah, no kidding!

1:17:58.841 --> 1:18:00.752
Whoa...!

1:18:02.428 --> 1:18:04.009
But won't that bewilderbeast

1:18:04.096 --> 1:18:06.712
just take control
of these guys, too?

1:18:06.807 --> 1:18:09.640
They're babies!
They don't listen to anyone.

1:18:09.727 --> 1:18:11.809
Yeah. Just like us.

1:18:11.896 --> 1:18:14.478
This is... whoal...
Very dangerous!

1:18:18.986 --> 1:18:22.979
Some might suggest
this is poorly conceived!

1:18:23.073 --> 1:18:25.029
Well, it's a good thing
that I never listen.

1:18:25.117 --> 1:18:26.527
Whoal

1:18:26.619 --> 1:18:27.825
so...

1:18:27.912 --> 1:18:30.324
What is your... plan?

1:18:30.414 --> 1:18:33.247
Get toothless back
and kick drago's...

1:18:33.334 --> 1:18:34.824
Heads up!

1:18:34.919 --> 1:18:36.910
And that thing.

1:18:37.004 --> 1:18:38.835
Whoa... owl!

1:18:59.526 --> 1:19:00.526
Oh! On...

1:19:00.611 --> 1:19:02.476
Ah, that's a good boy.

1:19:06.784 --> 1:19:08.240
Uh...

1:19:08.327 --> 1:19:10.158
W-w-watch the furniture!

1:19:10.246 --> 1:19:12.237
Where are you going?

1:19:29.682 --> 1:19:32.640
Your chief... is dead!

1:19:32.726 --> 1:19:35.263
- Stoick?
- Not possible!

1:19:35.354 --> 1:19:37.811
No one can protect you now!

1:19:52.079 --> 1:19:53.910
No.

1:19:54.623 --> 1:19:56.534
He took all the dragons.

1:19:58.294 --> 1:19:59.830
Distract the Alpha.

1:19:59.920 --> 1:20:02.502
Try to keep his focus
off of toothless.

1:20:02.589 --> 1:20:03.795
Uh, how?

1:20:03.882 --> 1:20:05.918
Have you forgotten
who you're riding with?

1:20:06.010 --> 1:20:09.468
There isn't a dragon alive
that I can't wrangle! Aah!

1:20:09.555 --> 1:20:11.755
- Except for this one...!
- Amateur.

1:20:13.434 --> 1:20:14.844
Hey, look! It's hiccup!

1:20:20.691 --> 1:20:22.477
What?

1:20:36.957 --> 1:20:38.618
Keep 'em coming!

1:20:38.709 --> 1:20:40.245
Black sheep, baby!

1:20:50.763 --> 1:20:52.503
Ten points!

1:20:54.266 --> 1:20:55.881
Uh-oh.

1:21:06.695 --> 1:21:08.651
I'm okay!

1:21:16.163 --> 1:21:19.530
You certainly are hard
to get rid of, I'll say that.

1:21:19.625 --> 1:21:21.536
Toothless...

1:21:21.627 --> 1:21:23.538
Hey.

1:21:23.629 --> 1:21:25.711
It's me, bud.

1:21:25.798 --> 1:21:27.038
It's me.

1:21:27.132 --> 1:21:29.168
It's me. I'm right here, bud.

1:21:29.259 --> 1:21:30.965
Come back to me.

1:21:33.013 --> 1:21:35.720
He's not yours anymore.

1:21:35.808 --> 1:21:37.969
He belongs to the Alpha.

1:21:38.060 --> 1:21:41.552
But, please,
o great dragon master,

1:21:41.647 --> 1:21:44.184
try... to take him.

1:21:44.274 --> 1:21:47.687
He will not miss a second time.

1:21:47.778 --> 1:21:49.860
It wasn't your fault, bud.

1:21:51.448 --> 1:21:53.780
They... made you do it.

1:22:03.210 --> 1:22:05.041
You'd never hurt him.

1:22:09.216 --> 1:22:12.458
You'd never hurt me.

1:22:15.764 --> 1:22:17.675
How are you doing that?

1:22:17.766 --> 1:22:21.054
Please.
You are my best friend, bud.

1:22:25.315 --> 1:22:27.101
My best friend.

1:22:32.781 --> 1:22:34.396
Attaboy! That's it!

1:22:34.491 --> 1:22:35.491
I'm here.

1:22:35.576 --> 1:22:37.066
Enough!

1:22:41.874 --> 1:22:42.874
Yeah!

1:22:42.958 --> 1:22:45.040
Hang on!

1:22:49.756 --> 1:22:51.417
Almost there, buddy,
almost there.

1:23:01.477 --> 1:23:02.967
Do something!

1:23:03.061 --> 1:23:05.017
We need to get those two apart.

1:23:15.324 --> 1:23:17.815
We gotta block him out,
toothless.

1:23:17.910 --> 1:23:19.616
Do you trust me, bud?

1:23:21.830 --> 1:23:23.491
We can do this.

1:23:23.582 --> 1:23:26.198
You... and me...

1:23:26.293 --> 1:23:27.874
As one.

1:23:30.506 --> 1:23:31.746
That's it.

1:23:31.840 --> 1:23:34.206
Now let's try this
one more time!

1:23:35.010 --> 1:23:38.047
Take him down, babe!

1:23:41.767 --> 1:23:42.847
Go get him.

1:23:45.145 --> 1:23:46.555
Take control of it!

1:23:49.233 --> 1:23:50.473
Shut it out, toothless.

1:23:50.567 --> 1:23:52.103
- Stop them!
- Now!

1:23:57.824 --> 1:23:58.824
Huh...?

1:24:15.509 --> 1:24:16.544
Not again.

1:24:18.762 --> 1:24:21.845
Toothless, it's now or never!

1:24:23.767 --> 1:24:25.052
Come on, bud!

1:24:27.396 --> 1:24:28.396
Hold on!

1:24:31.608 --> 1:24:33.894
Ya-ha! We did it!

1:24:42.077 --> 1:24:44.614
Hold him there, toothless.

1:24:44.705 --> 1:24:46.787
It's all over now.

1:24:48.500 --> 1:24:49.990
Oris it?

1:24:51.003 --> 1:24:52.743
Uh...

1:24:52.838 --> 1:24:53.838
Oh, no!

1:25:03.056 --> 1:25:04.592
No!

1:25:04.683 --> 1:25:07.595
No!

1:25:15.485 --> 1:25:16.520
Hiccup...

1:25:47.726 --> 1:25:49.136
He's challenging the Alpha!

1:25:49.227 --> 1:25:50.842
To protect you!

1:26:16.672 --> 1:26:19.664
No, no, no, no, no! No!

1:26:19.758 --> 1:26:21.669
Fight back! Fight!

1:26:21.760 --> 1:26:22.920
Fight!

1:26:25.514 --> 1:26:27.800
What's the matter with you!

1:26:31.144 --> 1:26:34.352
Hold your ground!
Hold the line now!

1:26:38.026 --> 1:26:39.186
Now do you get it?

1:26:39.277 --> 1:26:42.769
This is what it is
to earn a dragon's loyalty.

1:26:44.866 --> 1:26:46.572
Let this end now.

1:26:46.660 --> 1:26:47.900
Never!

1:26:47.994 --> 1:26:49.074
Come on!

1:26:57.796 --> 1:26:58.831
Huh?

1:27:12.310 --> 1:27:13.800
Fight!

1:27:47.387 --> 1:27:49.844
The Alpha... protects them all.

1:28:49.825 --> 1:28:51.861
You never cease
to amaze me, bud.

1:28:52.494 --> 1:28:54.109
Thank you.

1:28:57.290 --> 1:28:59.997
Toothless, you know
that doesn't wash out!

1:29:01.920 --> 1:29:04.662
- I knew you'd come back!
- You're back, my beauty!

1:29:04.756 --> 1:29:05.996
Oh! Onl

1:29:07.259 --> 1:29:08.374
stormfly!

1:29:11.429 --> 1:29:14.091
Oh, give me a cuddle, grumpy!

1:29:14.182 --> 1:29:15.592
Oh!

1:29:17.602 --> 1:29:19.138
Who's my little Princess!

1:29:19.229 --> 1:29:20.810
Don't you ever leave
again, hookfang.

1:29:20.897 --> 1:29:23.730
Oh, you are. Yes, you are.
I missed you...

1:29:23.817 --> 1:29:25.023
Oh, barf...

1:29:25.110 --> 1:29:26.771
Not you!

1:29:29.281 --> 1:29:30.396
That was some

1:29:30.490 --> 1:29:32.572
pretty fine dragon-wrangling
back there.

1:29:32.659 --> 1:29:34.274
You'd make a good trapper.

1:29:34.369 --> 1:29:35.825
Whoa.

1:29:35.912 --> 1:29:38.870
You know... skullcrusher
is gonna need somebody

1:29:38.957 --> 1:29:40.197
to look after him now.

1:29:40.834 --> 1:29:41.949
Me?

1:29:46.214 --> 1:29:47.420
I'd be honored.

1:29:48.508 --> 1:29:50.544
Oh, your father,

1:29:50.635 --> 1:29:53.001
he'd be every bit
as proud as I am.

1:29:53.096 --> 1:29:54.836
Thank you.

1:29:54.931 --> 1:29:56.967
I'm really glad
you're here, mom.

1:29:57.058 --> 1:29:59.049
And here ['ll stay.

1:30:00.562 --> 1:30:02.473
See?

1:30:02.564 --> 1:30:04.054
I told you it was in here.

1:30:04.149 --> 1:30:06.060
Ah, ha, ha.

1:30:06.151 --> 1:30:07.732
You're still doing that one.

1:30:07.819 --> 1:30:09.434
That's hilarious.

1:30:09.529 --> 1:30:12.066
- Come here, you.
- Mm!

1:30:12.157 --> 1:30:13.442
Ooh!

1:30:43.688 --> 1:30:45.849
The chief has come home!

1:30:49.611 --> 1:30:50.942
Yeah!

1:30:52.530 --> 1:30:54.646
Long live the chief!

1:30:54.741 --> 1:30:59.030
Long live the chief!
Long live the chief!

1:30:59.120 --> 1:31:01.202
Long live the chief!

1:31:11.800 --> 1:31:13.336
Yeah! Ha-hal

1:31:15.303 --> 1:31:16.509
ah...

1:31:17.889 --> 1:31:19.845
Yah-ha-ha-hal

1:31:23.812 --> 1:31:25.894
this... is berk.

1:31:26.856 --> 1:31:28.392
A bit trampled and busted

1:31:28.483 --> 1:31:31.145
and covered in ice,
but it's home.

1:31:31.236 --> 1:31:32.646
It's our home.

1:31:36.992 --> 1:31:40.405
Those who attacked us
are relentless and crazy.

1:31:40.495 --> 1:31:42.611
But those who stopped them?

1:31:42.706 --> 1:31:45.322
Oh... even more so!

1:31:47.585 --> 1:31:51.169
We may be small in numbers,
